'''Lee Hye-ri''' (born June 9, 1994),<ref>http://people.search.naver.com/search.naver?where=nexearch&query=%ED%98%9C%EB%A6%AC&sm=ppl_cts&ie=utf8&key=PeopleService&os=189558</ref> si fiican loogu yaqaanno magac ahaan '''Hyeri''', waa atariisho Koonfur Kuuriya ah, heesaa, iyo shaqsiyadda telefishanka.  Waxay caan ku noqotay xubinta ugu yar ee kooxda gabdhaha [[Girl's Day]], waxaana warbaahinta Koonfur Kuuriya loogu magacaabay "Walaasha Yar ee Qaranka" sababtuna waxay tahay sumcaddeeda weyn kadib markii ay ka soo muuqatay ''Real Men'' (2014).<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20201111203236/http://ilyo.co.kr/?ac=article_view&entry_id=90349</ref><ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20170203163141/http://www.sisaweek.com/news/articleView.html?idxno=33265</ref><ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20210420032810/https://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=109&aid=0002952539</ref>

Waxay markii dambe caan ku noqotay doorkeedii hoggaamineed ee taxanaha telefishanka ''Reply 1988'' (2015), kaas oo ahaa taxanaha ugu sarreeya ee taariikhda telefishanka fiilada Kuuriya wakhtigaas.  Waxay gashay kaalinta saddexaad liiska ''[[Forbes]]''  Caannimada Awoodda Kuuriya ee 2016, waana mid ka mid ah dhiirrigeliyeyaasha ganacsi ee ugu mushaharka badan Koonfur Kuuriya.<ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20160226175628/http://koreajoongangdaily.joins.com/news/article/Article.aspx?aid=3015489</ref><ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20160127104438/http://kpopherald.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=201601261821372489506_2</ref><ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20160125092950/http://kpopherald.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=201601240944380583152_2</ref><ref>https://web.archive.org/web/20210420032834/https://media.adpnut.com/cgi-bin/PelicanC.dll?impr?pageid=03L1&out=script</ref>

